WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Brikon' is a Workbench game played on an 8 by 8 tile board. The
goal is to place 32 bricks, vertically or horizontally, in such a
way that there are no continuous straight lines between bricks,
from one edge of the board to the other.

  If the game seems simple, a little complication has been added:
one or more bricks (up to 8) are already placed on the game
board... and when a brick is placed, it cannot be moved later on.

  Have fun!

